      • copyDocumentType

        public DocumentType copyDocumentType(DocumentType existingDocType,
                            DocumentType newDocumentType)
        Copies following entries of existing DocumentType to the new DocumentType:-
        • Copies field type to existing DocumentType to the new DocumentType.
        • Copies page type of existing DocumentType to the new DocumentType.
        • Copies table info of existing DocumentType to the new DocumentType
        • Copies function keys of existing DocumentType to the new DocumentType
        Specified by:
        copyDocumentType in interface DocumentTypeService
        Parameters:
        existingDocType - DocumentType existing document from which function keys are to be copied.
        newDocumentType - DocumentType new document to which function keys are to be copied.
        Returns:
        DocumentTypecopy of existing document type with all parameters set or newDocumentType input parameter is returned if existing document type is null.
